articles.title: Man dies in Tampines accident 1 day before returning home to Malaysia - AsiaOne
articles.description: In a cruel twist of fate, a man died in a road accident in Tampines one day before he was due to return to his home in Malaysia via the Vaccinated Travel Lane. The 36-year-old aircraft technician was on his motorcycle when the accident occurred along Tampines…
